      },
      "flashin": {
        "alpha": [
          1,
          0
        ],
        "black": true,
        "delay": 1,
        "dur": 1
      },
      "say": "和{namecode:78}去商店的第二天，像往常一样在指挥室工作时，突然收到了一封邮件。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "bgm": "story-1",
      "bgmDelay": 2,
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "「您有空吗？」",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "actorName": "邮件",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "内容就只有这些，发件人显示的还是“匿名”——这时又收到了第二封邮件。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "「我马上就到」",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "actorName": "邮件",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "这是要来指挥室的意思么……总之先让这位匿名的发信人说清楚自己究竟是谁——",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "「我在喷泉前面」",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "actorName": "邮件",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "「我到楼里了」",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "actorName": "邮件",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "又收到两封邮件…看样子对方离自己越来越近了。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "最后该不会像鬼故事一样来一句“我就在你身后”吧…？这么想的瞬间，再次收到了一封邮件。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "「我在指挥室门口」",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "actorName": "邮件",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "读完这封邮件的同时，指挥室的门被敲响了。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "小心翼翼的来到门前，慢慢的打开门——",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "……对、对不起殿下。本来想用邮件跟您讨论一下补给仓库的事情，但是打字实在是有些难…",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "智能手机真的好难用……发邮件时也不知道为什么就变成“隐私模式”了…",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "我一直都不擅长应付电子设备之类的……怎么了殿下？看您好像松了口气的样子……？",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "{namecode:78}不解地望了过来。",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "总之，我想带您去看之前提到的那片空地，殿下您现在有空吗？",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "如果可以的话，请跟我来吧。",
      "actor": 305010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "跟着{namecode:78}走出办公室之后，先前的紧张感终于消失了……",
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "得好好教一下她怎么发邮件才行，这种事情再来几次的话对心脏可不好……",
      "blackBg": true,
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    }
  ],
